<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/19570327">儿童注意力问题与多动症 ADHD 研究状况如何？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="8062" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content"> 有很多文章涉及这个话题，特别是说电视、电子游戏、智能手机、iPad容易导致ADHD。也看到一些研究的介绍，如 <a href="http://www.switched.com/2010/07/06/too-much-time-screen-time-causes-attention-problems-in-class-st/" class=" external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer"><span class="invisible">http://www.</span><span class="visible">switched.com/2010/07/06</span><span class="invisible">/too-much-time-screen-time-causes-attention-problems-in-class-st/</span><span class="ellipsis"></span><i class="icon-external"></i></a> ；<br>也有指出这类研究结论有问题的，如 <a href="http://www.canada.com/health/million+children+misdiagnosed+with+ADHD+Study/3413493/story.html" class=" external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer"><span class="invisible">http://www.</span><span class="visible">canada.com/health/milli</span><span class="invisible">on+children+misdiagnosed+with+ADHD+Study/3413493/story.html</span><span class="ellipsis"></span><i class="icon-external"></i></a> 。据Kaiser Family Foundation 2003年的调查，美国0~6岁的儿童 91％ 观看电视，89%观看DVD，48%用过电脑，30％玩过游戏主机。国内的情况估计也差不多。<br><br><a href="http://newideas.net/" class=" external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer"><span class="invisible">http://</span><span class="visible">newideas.net/</span><span class="invisible"></span><i class="icon-external"></i></a> 系统收集了很多材料，不过大多不在我关心的方向上。<br><br>有没有专业人士能给系统的介绍一下这个领域的研究现状、历史和主要观点流派？ </div>


</div>
